movie.title_english: LEGO DC Super Hero Girls: Super-villain High
movie.title_long: LEGO DC Super Hero Girls: Super-villain High (2018)
movie.description_intro: The girls discover a new high school, but soon realize that the school is for supervillains. Wonder Woman, Harley Quinn, Poison Ivy, Supergirl, Batgirl, Katana, and Bumblebee come together to help those that are being used by the new school to commit crimes.

movies.title: Game Over, Man!
movies.summary: Alexxx, Darren, and Joel are three losers who work as maids at a hotel and all have problems. Alexxx is an impulsive and immature manchild. Darren constantly vapes to avoid the world around. Joel is a closeted gay man whose sexuality is obvious to everyone except himself. When word gets out that social media influencer Bae Awadi is coming to their hotel, the three try to pitch their game idea to him. But when terrorists arrive and take hostages, including Bae, the three must man up and save the day.

movies.title: The Gourmet Detective Eat, Drink & Be Buried
movies.title_english: The Gourmet Detective Eat, Drink & Be Buried
movies.title_long: The Gourmet Detective Eat, Drink & Be Buried (2017)
movies.summary: A wealthy family with a storied past and a large sprawling estate, hires Henry to oversee the menu for an annual summer gala. When one of the host's sons dies at the event, Maggie and Henry are on the case once again, finding themselves in the crosshairs of a bitter feud between heirs to a family fortune.

movies.title: Malone
movies.summary: A former CIA-assassin, on the run from his former employers, gets stranded in a small Wyoming town and stays to help a local farmer and his daughter fight the corrupt sheriff who's under the thumb of a ruthless land developer out to evict all the farmers from their homes.

movies.title: Cabal
movies.summary: Cabal is about a military assassin, code named Dragonfly, that is hired to hunt and eliminate a serial killer, Sallos, preying on innocent young girls. While on assignment he learns that there's a much more sinister danger than he had anticipated.
